FIELD.name: D (pc)
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Distance to the object given in parsec.

FIELD.name: Err D (pc)
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Error in the Distance to the object

FIELD.name: Teff
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Effective temperature of the model in Kelvin

FIELD.name: Ftot
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Total flux of the star (outside the wavelength range covered by the observations, the flux has been inferred using the best fitting model)

FIELD.name: Ferr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Error in the total flux of the star (where the flux corresponding to the observed filters has been substituted by the observed ones)

FIELD.name: Fobs/Ftot
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Fraction of the total flux corresponding to the observations

FIELD.name: Lbol
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Bolometric luminosity of the object in solar units. This is calculated using the Ftot and the distance given by the user

FIELD.name: Lberr
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Error in the bolometric luminosity of the object in solar units.

FIELD.name: MaxLam
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Last wavelength used in the fitting.

FIELD.name: Nfit
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Number of points used in the fitting.

FIELD.name: e_Teff
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the effective temperature of the model in Kelvin

FIELD.name: e_logg
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the logarithm of the surface gravity

FIELD.name: e_Meta.
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Uncertainty in the metallicity for the model

FIELD.name: Teff_min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minimum value for the Effective temperature of the model in Kelvin

FIELD.name: Teff_max
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Maximum value for the Effective temperature of the model in Kelvin

FIELD.name: logg_min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minimum value for the Logarithm of the surface gravity

FIELD.name: logg_max
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Maximum value for the Logarithm of the surface gravity

FIELD.name: Meta_min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minimum value for the Metallicity for the model

FIELD.name: Meta_max
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Maximum value for the Metallicity for the model

FIELD.name: excfit
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Filter where infrared excess seems to start when comparing observed photometry with the best fit model.

FIELD.name: Age_min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minimum value for the Object age in Gyr

FIELD.name: Age_max
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Maximum value for the Object age in Gyr

FIELD.name: Mass_min
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Minimum value for the Object mass in Msun

FIELD.name: Mass_max
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Maximum value for the Object mass in Msun
